Jean Bradin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Bradin 0 Jean Bradin (30 May 1899 – 7 October 1969) was a French actor. Bradin was born in the 5th arrondissement of Paris and died in the 15th arrondissement of Paris. Jean_Bradin ( 30_May_1899 – 7_October_1969 ) was a_French_actor .
